292
00:12:07.500 --> 00:12:11.400
symptom assessment as the guide?

293
00:12:11.400 --> 00:12:14.700
Well you have to make the diagnosis first.

294
00:12:14.700 --> 00:12:19.440
So you're going to sense the diagnosis of your COPD

295
00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:22.500
with the spirometry, then you're done.

296
00:12:22.500 --> 00:12:25.863
'Cause after that it's all symptom management, remember?

297
00:12:27.390 --> 00:12:30.150
But the guidelines definitely want you

298
00:12:30.150 --> 00:12:33.510
to do the spirometry first in order to make the diagnosis

299
00:12:33.510 --> 00:12:37.350
