340
00:14:09.540 --> 00:14:12.993
because of increased resistance to strep pneumonia.

341
00:14:13.950 --> 00:14:18.480
So that really depends on where you live.

342
00:14:18.480 --> 00:14:21.630
You can get this data from your local hospitals.

343
00:14:21.630 --> 00:14:24.120
The pharmacy department has a local,

344
00:14:24.120 --> 00:14:25.860
what they call an antibiogram.

345
00:14:25.860 --> 00:14:27.270
They're happy to share that with you

346
00:14:27.270 --> 00:14:28.620
and they may say, oh,

347
00:14:28.620 --> 00:14:32.280
in our community, the strep pneumo resistance

348
00:14:32.280 --> 00:14:35.070
to azithromycin is 44%.

349
00:14:35.070 --> 00:14:36.150
Well that's terrible.

350
00:14:36.150 --> 00:14:37.830
I wouldn't wanna use that drug.

351
00:14:37.830 --> 00:14:42.780
If it's 12% then absolutely you could consider it.

352
00:14:42.780 --> 00:14:45.120
<v ->Great I'll take back over, yes.</v>

353
00:14:45.120 --> 00:14:46.470
Several questions about do I need

354
00:14:46.470 --> 00:14:48.720
to memorize the Wells' criteria?

355
00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:51.300
I think no, you need to be generally aware of it

356
00:14:51.300 --> 00:14:53.040
because they're gonna give you slam dunks.

357
00:14:53.040 --> 00:14:55.620
They're gonna give you really low risk or really high risk.

358
00:14:55.620 --> 00:14:57.540
I don't think you need to know like how many points this,

359
00:14:57.540 --> 00:15:00.873
that and the other, but have some gestalt awareness of it.

360
00:15:01.860 --> 00:15:04.920
Couple questions about should we be starting Lovenox on all

361
00:15:04.920 --> 00:15:07.530
post-delivery patients within 12 hours?

362
00:15:07.530 --> 00:15:08.580
Definitely not.

363
00:15:08.580 --> 00:15:11.070
So this is only if a patient is already on

364
00:15:11.070 --> 00:15:13.650
anticoagulation going into the delivery.

365
00:15:13.650 --> 00:15:16.080
That was that slide about the 12 hour thing.

366
00:15:16.080 --> 00:15:19.830
So like if they had a DVT in pregnancy, you have to hold

367
00:15:19.830 --> 00:15:22.560
that Lovenox for them at the time of delivery.

368
00:15:22.560 --> 00:15:24.690
If they're having any kind of anesthetic

369
00:15:24.690 --> 00:15:26.670
or if they're getting a C-section.

370
00:15:26.670 --> 00:15:27.930
After a vaginal birth,

371
00:15:27.930 --> 00:15:31.590
you can restart whatever treatment you were doing around

372
00:15:31.590 --> 00:15:35.130
that six hour mark after a vaginal birth or six to 12 hours

373
00:15:35.130 --> 00:15:36.240
after a C-section.

374
00:15:36.240 --> 00:15:37.560
But don't get confused

375
00:15:37.560 --> 00:15:40.823
that everybody needs anticoagulation after birth.

376
00:15:40.823 --> 00:15:41.970
That is not accurate.

377
00:15:41.970 --> 00:15:44.320
Only if they were being treated for it already.

378
00:15:46.080 --> 00:15:47.370
If you have a cancer patient

379
00:15:47.370 --> 00:15:49.440
that's now considered a cancer survivor,

